    "### task 1\n",
    "In this exercise, I created different Python variables: integer, float, string, list, and dictionary. I used type() to check the type of each variable."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "80362776-2035-4ffa-b337-0eaa62eb4229",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Values: [10, 20, 30, 40]\n",
      "Alias: [10, 20, 30, 40]\n",
      "Original: [10, 20, 30, 40]\n",
      "Copy: [10, 20, 30, 40, 99]\n"
     ]
